text: Anaesthetis lanuginosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Baeckmann in 1903. It is known from Central Asia and Iran.BioLib.cz - Anaesthetis lanuginosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1903
title: Anaesthetis lanuginosa
